84
00:06:55,014 --> 00:06:58,814
Why not? Take this with you.

85
00:06:58,814 --> 00:07:02,494
- Give that to me.
- Oh, no! Please don't do that! It's Ha Neul's.

86
00:07:02,494 --> 00:07:04,054
